It would be great if admins could edit the set of stop words used by Lucene. There are reports (see [this answer|https://answers.atlassian.com/questions/37030881/how-to-change-confluence-lucene-stop-words]) of the standard set being non-sensical, and even issues concerning acronyms that coincide with a stop word ([CSP-174275|https://support.atlassian.com/browse/CSP-174275]).

Perhaps the General Configuration page could have a text area with all stop words, so admins would be able to easily add and delete from it?

